lead_paragraph: Lorena Ochoa of Mexico shot a five-under 68 in her first round as the No. 1-ranked player in the world, leaving her a stroke behind the leader, Stacy Prammanasudh, at the Corona Morelia Championship in Morelia, Mexico.
